quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  15,45,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tabatinya\tImana\tyabo\ty’ukuri\tbazoba\tbari\tmumirima n’amasoko y’amazi y’umusarara"
  15,46,Nimuyinjiremwo n’amahoro ntangere
  15,47,"Kandi\ttuzokuramwo\tamafundo\tyari\tmubikiriza\tvyabo,\tkandi\tbazoba abavandimwe bakundana bicaye hejuru y’inyegano zacami barabana"
  15,48,"Ntibazo korwako n’ingorane, canke ngo bakurwemwo"
  15,49,Babwire abantu banje yuko jewe mfise ikigongwe cinshi n’impuhwe zihagije
  15,50,Mu vy’ukuri ibihano vyanje n’ibihano bibabaza cane bimwe vy’akarorero
  15,51,Kandi ubabwire inkuru z’abashitsi b’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii)
  15,52,"Mugihe binjira munzu yiwe nukumuramutsa bavuze bati:- amahoro y’Imana abe kuri twese, nawe abishura nkuko nyene hanyuma aca avuga ati:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe turabinuvye"
  15,53,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- ntugire ubwoba twebwe tugufitiye inkuru nziza yuko uzokwibaruka ikibondo gifise ubumenyi buhanitse"
  15,54,"Nawe abishura ati:- munzaniye iyi nkuru mugihe namaze kuba umusaza, none n’iyihe nzira mumpaye y’izi nkuru nziza"
  15,55,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- tuguhaye iyi nkuru nziza y’ukuri, rero ntube mu bantu badebukirwa"
  15,56,"Nawe abishura ati:- ni nde adebukirwa kumigisha y’Umuremyi wiwe atari mu bantu bazimiye"
  15,57,"Yishura ati:- none ico mwipfuza n’igiki mwebwe mwatugendeye"
  15,58,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe twarungitswe kuri ba bantu bacumuye"
  15,59,"Dukuye mwo abakurikiye intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii), ntankeka twebwe tuzoba rokora uko bangana bose"
  15,60,"Dukuye mwo umukenyezi wiwe, niwe twibaza yuko yoba ari mu bantu bazo kwicara inyuma ya bose"